[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/roost">Roost</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/roost">Roost</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user lands and rests its body. It restores the user's HP by up to half of its max HP.</p>